title: Jeff Buckley Live in Concert - Huge Collection
description:
I stripped all of these from Youtube using clipconverter.cc. (most were just audio) They have since been taken down, but I believe the original up-loader was MVGroup. Thanks all the same!

There are some real gems here. If you are a fan of Jeff, this will be well worth the time to grab. The quality isn't always top-notch, but beggars can't be choosers can we?

ENJOY! and please share anywhere! I've only posted this to piratebay, so if some one wanted to put it on other torrent sites, that would be great.

The initial upload might take a bit, but I'll seed this for awhile if it proves even a little popular. I hope there are still fans of Jeff around... his music should live forever.

R.I.P. Jeff.
